                <mxCell id="callout" value="⚠️ TLS Fragmentation Issue:&#10;&#10;AL2023 curl uses X25519MLKEM768&#10;→ 1522-byte Client Hello&#10;→ Exceeds 1460-byte TCP MSS&#10;→ TLS record fragments across 2 TCP segments&#10;→ NFW cannot extract SNI&#10;→ Pass rule doesn't match&#10;→ Traffic evades inspection" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=5;fontSize=10;fontColor=#333333;" parent="1" vertex="1">
